Property.Name: Description
Property.Value: FITINN is an Austrian fitness studio chain with currently 47 locations in Austria (as of November 2022), 3 in the Czech Republic, 4 in Slovenia, and 2 locations each in Slovakia and Italy. The company headquarters are located in Vienna, and the first studio was opened in 2004 at the main train station in Graz. Currently, with over 220,000 members, FITINN is the fitness chain with the most members in Austria with the most studios and is a classic fitness discounter (low monthly price, reduced offer on endurance and strength equipment).

Property.Name: Description
Property.Value: Welcome to LifeGym, the premier chain of gyms in Slovakia. Our state-of-the-art facilities feature a wide range of fitness equipment, including cardio machines, weight lifting machines, and free weights. We also offer a variety of group fitness classes, such as spinning, yoga, and aerobics, to help you stay motivated and reach your fitness goals. Our experienced personal trainers are available to provide one-on-one guidance and support to help you get the most out of your workouts. Join our community of fitness enthusiasts and start your journey towards a healthier, happier you today at LifeGym.

Property.Name: Description
Property.Value: Nobel gym is a newly opened leisure centre that offers its clients professional services in a modern environment. Our centre is designed for all those looking for a healthy lifestyle, quality training and relaxation. We founded Nobel Gym with the idea of creating a professional yet family environment where you and our trainers can achieve your physical goals, push your limits and enjoy the results not only in our gym but also in your personal life. We offer our visitors a fully air-conditioned space for strength, functional and relaxation group workouts in a friendly environment. For the little ones we have music and dance workshops and exercises to develop motor skills and movement. A reception area with a fresh bar and seating will make your workout more enjoyable and give you enegria for the day. We have modern changing rooms and showers which are free for our clients to use.

Property.Name: Description
Property.Value: Welcome to the largest and highest quality fitness centre network in Slovakia! Golem Club is synonymous with fitness, relaxation and healthy lifestyle. Since the beginning of its operation, it has been offering a new way of perceiving fitness to the general public. Accessibility, pleasant environment, state-of-the-art machinery, new forms of training, individual approach to each client. After registration you will receive a Golem card, which serves as a client identifier, so you will not be allowed to enter the premises without it. Two entries on one card are not possible, each client has his own card.
